item.description: Please check out Christine's Directions to the trail head parking area. This is a great trail and can be as short or long as you like. It has little dipping area's for the dogs and blueberries are everywhere.
item.how_to_find_us: I'll be @ the trail head in a chevy Tracker. WOOf sticker on back
